SQL_STMT_U.val: SELECT A.ITEMCODE,ITEMNAME,SUM(QUANTITY) QUANTITY FROM FCT1 A LEFT JOIN OITM B ON A.ITEMCODE = B.ItemCode WHERE ABSID = :1 GROUP BY A.ITEMCODE,ItemName
SELECT BPLId,ITEMCODE,H.ObjType,QUANTITY,H.DocDate,H.DocEntry,H.DocNum,D.LineNum FROM :3 H JOIN :4 D ON H.DOCENTRY = D.DOCENTRY WHERE H.BplId = :1 and H.DocDate = ':2'
SELECT ROW_NUMBER() OVER(order BY ItemNAME),* FROM ( SELECT ITEMNAME,SUM(QUANTITY) AS QUANTITY FROM FCT1 A LEFT JOIN OITM B ON A.ITEMCODE = B.ITEMCODE where absid = :1 GROUP BY ITEMNAME) A
DELETE FCT1 WHERE ABSID :1 ; DELETE FCT2 WHERE ABSID :1 ; DELETE FCT3 WHERE ABSID :1 ; DELETE FCT4 WHERE ABSID :1

select DocEntry, DocNum, ObjType, DocDate, CardCode, NumAtCard, Ref2, Comments, BplId, U_IDU_Kode_PT 'Consignee', GroupNum, DocStatus from OIGE WHERE DocNum in (Select DocNum from FCT4 where Flag=1 and AbsId = :1 )

SELECT ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY M.ITEMNAME) Sort, M.ITEMNAME, F.QUANTITY, O.UOMCODE FROM ( SELECT ITEMCODE, SUM(QUANTITY) QUANTITY FROM FCT1 where AbsID = :1 GROUP BY ITEMCODE ) F LEFT JOIN OITM M ON F.ITEMCODE = M.ITEMCODE LEFT JOIN OUOM O ON O.UOMENTRY = M.IUOMENTRY ORDER BY Sort ASC
SELECT ROW_NUMBER() OVER(order BY ItemNAME),* FROM ( SELECT ITEMNAME,SUM(QUANTITY) AS QUANTITY FROM FCT1 A LEFT JOIN OITM B ON A.ITEMCODE = B.ITEMCODE where absid = :1 GROUP BY ITEMNAME) A
